text: Ramachandra Achar from the Carleton University, Ottawa, ON, Canada was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for contributions to interconnect and signal integrity analysis in high-speed designs. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Carleton University faculty Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
